                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Less effective with extremely dry or damaged skin.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Requires regular calibration for consistent performance</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <br />

                        <h3>Ultrasonic Fingerprint Scanners</h3>
                        <p>Ultrasonic fingerprint scanners utilize high-frequency sound waves to capture the detailed fingerprint data. When a finger is placed on the scanner, ultrasonic pulses are emitted, penetrating the skin to gather information from the valleys and ridges. The reflected sound waves are then processed to create a comprehensive 3D fingerprint image.</p>

                        <br />

                        <p><strong>Key Features of Ultrasonic Scanners</strong></p>
                        <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                            <p><strong>Superior Detail:</strong> Captures the high-resolution images, including depth information.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                            <p><strong>Environmental Resilience:</strong> Performs well in a variety of conditions, including moisture.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                            <p><strong>Difficult to Spoof:</strong> More Secure against the replication attempts.</p>
                        </div>

                        <br />

                        <p><strong>Ideal Applications of Ultrasonic Fingerprint Scanner</strong></p>
                        <p>Ultrasonic Scanner is particularly well-suited for:</p>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>High-End Smartphones</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Banking Security</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Government Security</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Military Application</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <br />

                        <p><strong>Benefits of Ultrasonic Fingerprint Scanner</strong></p>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Robust and difficult to spoof</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Works well with the wet, oily, or dirty finger</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-xxl-12 col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>It is ideal for integration in displays as it can read the fingerprints through thin materials such as glass.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <br />

                        <p><strong>Limitation of Ultrasonic Fingerprint Scanner</strong></p>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
