                                <div class="blog_sub_point_box">
                                    <p>Works in a wide range of environmental conditions.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <br />

                        <p><strong>Limitation of Thermal Fingerprint Scanner </strong></p>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-xxl-6 col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-12">
